    {
      "id": "69e49053623f90fde213e9d5",
      "text": "名言・格言・キャッチフレーズをリンクにする",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776586837
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053a2",
      "text": "from [Scrapboxのリンクは実質強調表現]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776586837
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4ca6f0000000000c0356d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776601710,
      "updated": 1776601710
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053a4",
      "text": "[/support-doc-jp/名言・格言・キャッチフレーズをリンクにする]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776586837
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053a5",
      "text": "\t2023年頃に公開されたページ",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776586837
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4ca720000000000c0356e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776601714,
      "updated": 1776601715
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053a6",
      "text": "> 良いフレーズがあった時",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776601712
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053a7",
      "text": ">  普通のエディタでは、太字にしたり、文字を大きくしたりするが",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776601712
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053a8",
      "text": ">  Cosenseでは[空リンク]にすると良い[/support-doc-jp/shokai.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776601712
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053a9",
      "text": ">  [https://scrapbox.io/files/65bc9840437ff60025fa1747.gif]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776601712
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053aa",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776601712
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053ab",
      "text": "> 人間はページタイトルは思い出せなくても、[格言]・[名言]めいたフレーズなら思い出せる",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776601712
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053ac",
      "text": ">  リンクすることで、印象的な表現が[QuickSearch]で検索できるように",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776601712
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053ad",
      "text": ">  見つかる確率が格段に上がります",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776601712
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053ae",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776601712
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053af",
      "text": "> これが世間では[道のメタファー]と呼ばれている、Cosense独自の検索方法です[shokai.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776601712
    },
    {
      "id": "69e490530000000000e053b0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1776586837,
      "updated": 1776586837
    },
    {
      "id": "69e4cae60000000000c0356f",
      "text": "[赤リンクの利点]",
